thread.title: Marie

author: Marie
title: Marie
text: The entire process of placing our home on the market and leading up to Auction day was managed with ultimate professionalism and proficiency by our agents. Sound advice, regular updates and efficient management of all matters pertaining to the sale could not have been handled better. Arch and David from the Fitzroy office are the consummate professionals - a perfect balance of expertise; informed knowledge of the market - stalwarts with an unfailing passion for what they do.
